---
title: One-Pan Trattoria Shrimp & Tortelloni Bake with a Crispy Parmesan Panko Topping
description: Think a cheesy stuffed pasta can’t get any better? What about baking it in a creamy sauce with a crispy topping? In this recipe, we toss cheese-stuffed tortelloni in an herby tomato cream sauce, then top with Parmesan and panko breadcrumbs. Once broiled, it turns into a showstopping topping that’ll earn you plenty of oohs and aahs from your lucky fellow diners.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/63b5b509d6e607d9130c959d-66a31f0c.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/one-pan-trattoria-shrimp-tortelloni-bake-63b5b509d6e607d9130c959d-f6ad7995.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/one-pan-trattoria-shrimp-and-tortelloni-bake-63b5b509d6e607d9130c959d
course: main course
time required: 25 minutes
servings: 2
nutrition:
  calories: 880 kcal
  fat: 43 g
  saturated fat: 21 g
  carbohydrates: 77 g
  sugar: 15 g
  protein: 40 g
  fiber: 6 g
  sodium: 2690 mg
cuisine: Italian
author: HelloFresh
